prodNameC: 可芮斯輪狀病毒快速檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.Rota-Strip strips:
   Each strip is sensitized with a guinea pig anti-Rotavirus polyclonal serum and a goat anti-mouse IgG polyserum.
   The anti-Rotavirus conjugate is produced with a mouse monoclonal antibody directed against the human Rotavirus Group A VP6 antigens.
2.Dilution buffer:
   Saline solution buffered to pH 7.5 with TRIS and containing EDTA, NaN3 (<0.1%), a detergent, and charged proteins.
